      "policy_update": "A New York State Medicaid Update emphasizes that claim level identifiers are required for any 340B-purchased drug billed to NYRx, Medicaid Managed Care Plan, or as a secondary claim, to ensure rebates are not collected for these drugs [New York State Medicaid Update June 2023 Volume 39 Number 11:6 - 2023-06-01]."
    }
